high_descs: Turn around towards the windows, turn left towards the coffee maker, turn right towards the loaf of bread on the counter, and then look up towards the cabinets.
Open the right cabinet and take out a green cup.
Take a step to the right to find the microwave above the stove.
Warm up the cup and take it back out of the microwave.
Take a step to the left and look up to the cabinet above the bread.
Place the cup back into the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Warm up the cup inside the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the wall, hang a left, head to the counter, turn left and cross the room to face the silver dishwasher and counter top to your right.
Pick up a green glass next to the vase from inside the top right cabinet above the loaf of bread and close the door.
Turn right and walk towards the silver stove on your left side.
Place the green glass on the right side inside the microwave above the stove, heat for three seconds, remove the heated glass and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the counter to the left of the stove.
Open the tall cabinet above the counter to the left of the microwave, place the heated glass to the right of the silver vase and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated glass in a tall cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and go left and then left again to stand at the counter in front of all of the utensils.
Open the cupboard above and take out the green vase.
Go right and stand in front of the microwave.
Put the vase in the microwave, turn it on and then take it out and shut the door.
Move to the left and stand in front of the cupboards to the left of the stove.
Open the upper cabinet and put the green vase in the cupboard to the right of the other one.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated vase in the cabinet.
